name: Skirt Tail
description:
Another mixed bag. Mainly trained on images of high-low skirts/skirt tails and a few other variations. It trained some of the girls too so even though this experiment didn't go as intended I like what it produces, mostly.

Weight: 0.9 and lower

Planning for another version in the future with strictly high-low skirts and better prompting. For now these prompts below may help with some issues you might face; especially the negative prompts I've added for example.

Helpful Prompts

Centered
Full body (higher weight)
Dress
Frills/Center frills
Skirt_tail
Various colors
Thighhighs/Stockings
High heels/Heels/Footwear/Thigh boots/High heel boots/Shoes

Negative Prompts:

Out of frame
Head out of frame
Close Up
Cropped
Border
Bare legs
White background/Simple background
See-through legwear
Skinny/Annorexic
Lantern
Tail
Cat Girl
Facial Mark
Forehead Mark
Forehead Jewel
Cane
Hat
Hairpin
1girl
